OL,3,CNI health trusts deliver warning over
OL,4,Cdangers of further service cuts
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's health trusts have
OL,7,Fwarned that delivering multi-million
OL,8,Fpound savings in 2025 will have a
OL,9,Fdetrimental impact on services.
OL,11,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt has said
OL,12,Fthe trusts may have to find
OL,13,F#200million of savings for a second
OL,14,Fyear amid ongoing budget pressures.
OL,16,FIt comes as hospitals attempt to
OL,17,Frecover from a difficult number of
OL,18,Fweeks dealing with winter illnesses.
