OL,3,CNI health trusts deliver warning over
OL,4,Cdangers of further service cuts
OL,6,FThe Emergency Department at Causeway
OL,7,FHospital remains over capacity with
OL,8,Fsome patients still waiting up to five
OL,9,Fdays for a bed.
OL,11,FProfessor Mark Taylor, NI
OL,12,FConfederation for Health and Social
OL,13,FCare said: "We talked last week about
OL,14,Fthe perfect storm and it looks as if
OL,15,Fthat storm is going to continue and
OL,16,Fthis time in relation to finances.
OL,18,F"The trusts made #200million of
OL,19,Fsavings last year and now the
OL,20,Fexpectation is that they make another
OL,21,F#200million of savings.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
