OL,6,F"What do we stop? What can we
OL,7,Fcontinue? The difficulty is when you
OL,8,Fare asked to continue to make that
OL,9,Fdegree of funding constraint in a
OL,10,Fsystem that we have not transformed it
OL,11,Fis going to be very difficult."
OL,13,FTrusts are under pressure to free up
OL,14,Fward beds to improve the flow through
OL,15,Ftheir hospitals.
OL,17,FCauseway has been reducing the need
OL,18,Ffor hospital admission with same day
OL,19,Fcare units such as the Acute
OL,20,FAmbulatory Unit and Frailty Direct
OL,21,FAssessment Unit.
