OL,6,FSteven Kelly, lead nurse in the Acute
OL,7,FAmbulatory Unit said: "It takes some
OL,8,Fpressure off the ED.
OL,10,F"Whenever we are going down first
OL,11,Fthing in the morning when the ED has
OL,12,Fbeen full to capacity overnight we are
OL,13,Fable to take a few patients that we
OL,14,Fknow we can see."
OL,16,FInstead of long waiting in the ED and
OL,17,Fa hospital stay, patients in same day
OL,18,Fcare units are able to be diagnosed,
OL,19,Ftreated and sent home at the end of
OL,20,Fthe day.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
