OL,3,CNI health trusts deliver warning over
OL,4,Cdangers of further service cuts
OL,6,FEmily McIntosh, Consultant
OL,7,Fgeriatrician, said: "At the moment our
OL,8,FEDs are full to bursting and we can
OL,9,Fbring them straight here instead and
OL,10,Fthey can have access to the expertise
OL,11,Fthat they need straightaway rather
OL,12,Fthan having to wait for a day or two.
OL,14,F"Every time that you wait for more
OL,15,Fthan 24 hours if you have come into
OL,16,Fhospital, you can add up to five days
OL,17,Fto the length of your stay."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
