OL,6,FThe hospital's Surgical Department is
OL,7,Falso reducing patients length of stay
OL,8,Fthrough a same day care facility but
OL,9,Flack of capacity due to lack of
OL,10,Ffunding is hindering progress.
OL,12,FConsultant surgeon James Patterson
OL,13,Fsaid: "We are actually running over
OL,14,Four funded capacity at the minute to
OL,15,Fhelp with our emergency care.
OL,17,F"If those were all funded that would
OL,18,Fimprove it. We also would need some
OL,19,Finvestment in terms of staffing but
OL,20,Fgetting the funded sessions would be a
OL,21,Fstep forward."
